statements: SELECT * FROM parking_spots;
SELECT spot_id, spot_location, availability FROM parking_spots WHERE area_id = 3;
SELECT spot_type, COUNT(*) FROM parking_spots GROUP BY spot_type;
SELECT * FROM parking_spots WHERE spot_location LIKE '%mall%';
SELECT area_id, COUNT(*) FROM parking_spots WHERE availability = 'occupied' GROUP BY area_id;
SELECT spot_id, spot_type, spot_location FROM parking_spots WHERE area_id = 1 ORDER BY spot_location ASC
SELECT * FROM parking_spots WHERE availability = 'available' AND spot_type = 'covered' ORDER BY spot_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_spots, area_id FROM parking_spots GROUP BY area_id ORDER BY total_spots DESC
SELECT spot_id, availability, spot_location FROM parking_spots WHERE spot_type = 'open' AND availability = 'full' ORDER BY spot_id ASC
SELECT DISTINCT spot_type FROM parking_spots ORDER BY spot_type ASC LIMIT 3
SELECT * FROM parking_spaces;
SELECT available, location FROM parking_spaces WHERE available = TRUE;
SELECT parking_space_id, location FROM parking_spaces ORDER BY parking_space_id DESC;
SELECT location, available FROM parking_spaces WHERE location LIKE 'A%';
SELECT * FROM parking_logs ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM parking_spaces WHERE available = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM parking_spaces WHERE location LIKE 'A%';
SELECT location, available FROM parking_spaces WHERE location = 'Near Entrance';
SELECT * FROM parking_spaces WHERE parking_space_id BETWEEN 10 AND 20;
SELECT location, available FROM parking_spaces ORDER BY available DESC, location ASC;
SELECT * FROM parking_lot;
SELECT location,capacity FROM parking_lot WHERE capacity > 50;
SELECT parking_lot_id FROM parking_lot ORDER BY parking_lot_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM parking_history WHERE is_reserved = TRUE ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT parking_lot_id, cost_per_hour FROM parking_cost WHERE currency = 'USD';
SELECT * FROM parking_lot;
SELECT location, capacity FROM parking_lot WHERE capacity > 50 ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT parking_lot_id, location, capacity, available_spots FROM parking_lot WHERE available_spots < capacity;
SELECT parking_history_id, parking_lot_id, timestamp FROM parking_history WHERE is_reserved = true ORDER BY timestamp ASC;

SELECT parking_lot.location, parking_cost.cost_per_hour, parking_cost.currency FROM parking_lot JOIN parking_cost ON parking_lot.parking_lot_id = parking_cost.parking_lot_id WHERE parking_cost.cost_per_hour > 5;
SELECT * FROM parking_lot;
SELECT parking_spot_id, spot_location FROM parking_lot WHERE availability = true;
SELECT * FROM parking_history ORDER BY date_time DESC;
SELECT parking_spot_id, rate, currency FROM parking_rates WHERE rate > 5.00;
SELECT user_id, preferred_location, notify FROM user_parking_preferences WHERE max_distance < 10.00;
SELECT * FROM parking_lot ORDER BY spot_location DESC, parking_spot_id ASC;
SELECT parking_spot_id, spot_location, availability FROM parking_lot WHERE availability = TRUE ORDER BY parking_spot_id DESC;
SELECT history_id, parking_spot_id, date_time, status FROM parking_history WHERE status = 'occupied' ORDER BY date_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, preferred_location, max_distance, notify FROM user_parking_preferences WHERE max_distance > 5 ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT p.parking_spot_id, p.spot_location, r.rate, r.currency FROM parking_lot p INNER JOIN parking_rates r ON p.parking_spot_id = r.parking_spot_id WHERE r.currency = 'USD';
SELECT * FROM parking_lots;
SELECT location, total_spaces, status FROM parking_lots WHERE available_spaces > 0;
SELECT * FROM parking_spaces ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT user_id, full_name, license_plate FROM parking_users WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT transaction_id, start_time, end_time FROM parking_transactions WHERE user_id = 456 ORDER BY start_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM parking_lots LIMIT 5;
SELECT location, total_spaces, available_spaces FROM parking_lots ORDER BY available_spaces DESC;

SELECT pl.location, ps.location AS space_location, pu.full_name AS user_name FROM parking_lots pl JOIN parking_spaces ps ON pl.parking_lot_id = ps.lot_id JOIN parking_users pu ON pu.user_id = ps.parking_space_id;
SELECT pl.location, COUNT(ps.parking_space_id) AS occupied_spaces FROM parking_lots pl JOIN parking_spaces ps ON pl.parking_lot_id = ps.lot_id WHERE ps.availability = 'occupied' GROUP BY pl.location;

SELECT pu.full_name, pt.start_time, pl.location AS lot_location FROM parking_users pu JOIN parking_transactions pt ON pu.user_id = pt.user_id JOIN parking_spaces ps ON pt.parking_space_id = ps.parking_space_id JOIN parking_lots pl ON ps.lot_id = pl.parking_lot_id ORDER BY pt.start_time DESC;
